createdFlavors.message: It's like a circus in your mouth.
I love blueberry cake it is my favorite.
It's like a vacation in your mouth.
I tried the new Coca Cola coffee drink and think that the snow cone will taste similar.
When I was little my mom would always melt butter over our blueberry muffins as soon as they came out of the oven. I feel like this combo would taste very similar.

reviews.message: OMG the strawberry cheesecake snow cone is to die for!!
Took my kids here and they loved it. So happy to have a snow cone place in our town!
My kids love the sour gummi worm flavor! Highly recommend!
Can't get enough of their Key Lime Pie snow cone!
Always get your snow cone stuffed with ice cream! You won't regret it.
Not only do they have amazing snow cones but they sell food too! Best place in Memphis.
